                </div>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 mt-12 lg:mt-0">
          <div class="relative">
            <img src={getAssetUrl('images/book-cover.png')} alt="The Sixth Wood Book Cover" class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-2xl border border-emerald-800/30">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-emerald-900/20 to-transparent rounded-lg"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Book Overview -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-400 mb-4 font-['Cinzel']">
          A World of Harmonic Magic
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          In a world where six schools of harmony once flourished, one has been suppressed for generations.
          Now, a young student must rediscover the forbidden sixth tradition to save her world.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-emerald-800/30">
          <div class="text-emerald-400 text-4xl mb-4">üå≥</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-400 mb-3 font-['Cinzel']">The Six Arbories</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg">
            Elm, Oak, Birch, Ash, Fir, and the forbidden Yew‚Äîeach represents a different approach to harmonic magic,
            with their own traditions, strengths, and secrets.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-emerald-800/30">
          <div class="text-emerald-400 text-4xl mb-4">‚ö°</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-400 mb-3 font-['Cinzel']">Threshold Harmonics</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg">
            The suppressed magic of the Yew tradition allows practitioners to work at the boundaries between
            states of being‚Äîa power both wondrous and dangerous.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-emerald-800/30">
          <div class="text-emerald-400 text-4xl mb-4">üåä</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-400 mb-3 font-['Cinzel']">The Corrupted Whisper</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg">
            An ancient corruption threatens to consume the harmonic traditions, and only by embracing
            forbidden knowledge can it be contained.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Short Stories Preview -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-400 mb-4 font-['Cinzel']">
          Tales from I'lyr
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Explore the rich world of I'lyr through these standalone stories that reveal the depth
          and complexity of harmonic traditions across different regions and times.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">


        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-emerald-800/30 hover:border-emerald-600/50 transition-colors duration-200">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-800 to-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-6xl">üó∫Ô∏è</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-emerald-400 mb-2 font-['Cinzel']">Cartographer's Discovery</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-md mb-4">
              Asher Silverbrook uncovers dangerous secrets about the fragmentation of harmonic traditions.
            </p>
            <a href="/stories#cartographers-discovery" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 text-md font-semibold">
              Read More ‚Üí
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-purple-800/30 hover:border-purple-600/50 transition-colors duration-200">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-800 to-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-6xl">üå≤</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-400 mb-2 font-['Cinzel']">Whispers of the Cypress</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-md mb-4">
              A young Ebony practitioner discovers ancient Cypress-Stone harmonies threatened by institutional expansion.
            </p>
            <a href="/stories#whispers-of-the-cypress" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 text-md font-semibold">
              Read More ‚Üí
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>


      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a href="/stories" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors duration-200">
          Explore All Stories
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-900/50 to-slate-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-400 mb-6 font-['Cinzel']">
        Begin Your Journey
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
        Step into a world where music and magic intertwine, where ancient traditions hold the key to survival,
        and where one young woman's discovery will change everything.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/book" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors duration-200">
          Read The Sixth Wood
        </a>
        <a href="/about" class="border border-emerald-600 text-emerald-400 hover:bg-emerald-600 hover:text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors duration-200">
          Meet the Author
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

